<section class="team-section" style="padding: 80px 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #ffffff 100%);">
	<div style="max-width: 1280px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">

		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
			<h2 class="section-heading" style="font-family: var(--e-global-typography-vamtam_h1-font-family, 'Syne'), Sans-serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #000;">
				Meet Our Team
			</h2>
			<p class="section-subtitle" style="font-size: 18px; color: #777; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7;">
				We may be a small team, but we bring a focused and hands-on approach to everything we do.
			</p>
			<p class="section-subtitle" style="font-size: 17px; color: #777; max-width: 850px; margin: 20px auto 0; line-height: 1.7;">
				Led by our Founder, our work is built on clear vision, strong strategy, and a deep understanding of how brands grow in the digital space. Alongside, our Growth Strategist ensures every idea is brought to life through creative content, consistent execution, and performance-driven thinking.
			</p>
			<p class="section-subtitle" style="font-size: 17px; color: #777; max-width: 750px; margin: 15px auto 0; line-height: 1.7;">
				We work closely on every project, combining strategy and creativity to deliver results that are both impactful and measurable.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Team Cards Container -->
		<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin-top: 60px; max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">

			<!-- Team Member 1 -->
			<div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 18px; padding: 50px 40px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border: 1px solid #e8e8e8; transition: all 0.35s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
				<div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 4px; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #94d6f7 0%, #56b5f3 100%);"></div>
				<div style="text-align: left;">
					<div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
						<div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
						<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/120x120/1E88E5/FFFFFF?text=CN" alt="Chethana Nugawela" style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 4px solid #1E88E5;">
					</div>
					<h3 style="font-family: var(--e-global-typography-vamtam_h1-font-family, 'Syne'), Sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #000;">Chethana Nugawela</h3>
						<p style="font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #1E88E5; font-weight: 600; margin: 0;">Founder</p>
					</div>
					<p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
						Working closely with the team, leading strategy while ensuring strong client relationships and smooth project coordination. With a focus on growth and innovation, she combines strategic insight with hands-on involvement to deliver value in every project.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Team Member 2 -->
			<div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 18px; padding: 50px 40px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); border: 1px solid #e8e8e8; transition: all 0.35s ease; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
				<div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 4px; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #94d6f7 0%, #56b5f3 100%);"></div>
				<div style="text-align: left;">
					<div style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
						<div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
						<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/120x120/1E88E5/FFFFFF?text=MM" alt="Mahdiya Muflil" style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 4px solid: #1E88E5;">
					</div>
					<h3 style="font-family: var(--e-global-typography-vamtam_h1-font-family, 'Syne'), Sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #000;">Mahdiya Muflil</h3>
						<p style="font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #1E88E5; font-weight: 600; margin: 0;">Growth Strategist</p>
					</div>
					<p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
						Driving strategy, execution, and business development, she manages everything from content creation and social media to client coordination. With a focus on growth and results, she ensures every project aligns with the brand's vision while delivering meaningful impact for clients and the business.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

		<!-- Bottom CTA Section -->
		<div style="margin-top: 80px; padding: 50px 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A3D62 0%, #003366 100%); border-radius: 20px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
			<h3 style="font-family: var(--e-global-typography-vamtam_h1-font-family, 'Syne'), Sans-serif; color: #fff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;">
				Ready to Work With Us?
			</h3>
			<p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 30px; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
				Let's discuss how we can help build your digital presence and create campaigns that deliver real results for your brand.
			</p>
			<a href="contact.html" style="display: inline-block; background: #94d6f7; color: #003366; padding: 18px 45px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; transition: all 0.3s ease; box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(148,214,247,0.4);" onmouseover="this.style.background='#66c1ef'; this.style.transform='scale(1.05)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#94d6f7'; this.style.transform='scale(1)'">
